nit: Cleaner way to avoid collisions with `enum HTTPStatusCode` from /src/rpc/protocol.h which has things like `HTTP_OK`, and also to avoid the `EOF` `#define`. Also use more specific `enum` name:
```C++
enum HTTPReplyError {
    Ok,
    Timeout,
    ReadError,
    Eof,
};
```
